<div class="container">
  
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
  
      <h3>Solutions to the FIXML Case</h3>
      <% solutions = data.solutions_fixml  %>
      
      Case resources:
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://github.com/transformationtoolcontest/ttc2014-fixml">Description and case resources</a> (Github repository)</li>
        <li><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/ccc?key=0AqMVDh6v9Yx-dDV3M1h0UXd6dFRVdDNxa05ybUxkVGc&usp=sharing">Results from open peer reviewing of solutions</a> (Google Spreadsheet)</li>
        <li><a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/ttc2014-fixml">Discussion of solutions and open peer reviews</a> (Google Group)</li>
        <li><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1WfcpN4ptC9jphTIfhe0YlAyIdI2DCrAQlhIqp8SOeEM/viewform?usp=send_form">Scoresheet for judging of solutions</a> (Google Form)</li>
      </ul>

      <p>The following <%=solutions.size%> solutions were submitted for the FIXML case</a>.</p>
      
      <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-hover">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>
              Presentation<br/>
              (in PT/006)
            </th>
            <th>Tool</th>
            <th>Authors</th>
            <th>Artefacts</th>
            <th>Opponents</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% solutions.each_with_index do |solution, index| %>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <% slot = data.schedule_morning.find { |slot| slot.fixml == index } %>
                <%= slot.time %>
              </td>
              <td><strong><%=solution.tool%></strong></td>
              <td><%=solution.authors%></td>
              <td>
                <a href="/solutions/fixml/ttc2014_submission_<%=solution.pdf%>.pdf">PDF Description</a> <br/>
                
                <% if solution.share.empty? %>
                  <strong>No SHARE demo</strong>
                <% else %>
                  <a href="<%=solution.share%>">SHARE Demo</a>
                <% end %>
              </td>
              <td>
                <%=solutions[(index - 2) % solutions.length].authors%><br/>
                <%=solutions[(index - 1) % solutions.length].authors%>
              </td>
            </tr>
          <% end %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>